EVERGLADES DRAINAGE DISTRICT et al., Appellants, v. FLORIDA RANCH & DAIRY CORPORATION, a Delaware Corporation, Appellee. No. 7489. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Feb. 9, 1935. For former opinion, see 74 F.(2d) 914.

Before BRYAN, SIBLEY, and WALKER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appellee’s petition for rehearing, and motion filed Feb. 4, 1935, are denied.
